<h1 id="toc0"><span>Rose Labelle</span></h1>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
<div id="wiki-tabview-9ecfee7907a631b83a9fa85cc977ca75" class="yui-navset">
<ul class="yui-nav">
<li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>Information</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Where Can I Find More of Rose Labelle?</em></a></li>
</ul>
<div class="yui-content">
<div id="wiki-tab-0-0">
<p><strong>Name:</strong> <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/system:page-tags/tag/researcher-labelle#pages">Rose Labelle</a></p>
<p><strong>D.O.B.:</strong> 09/13/1980</p>
<p><strong>Security Clearance:</strong> Level 2 (Restricted)</p>
<p><strong>Position:</strong> Programmer, IT Specialist, Researcher of Anomalous Programs &amp; Computer Software</p>
<p><strong>Sites:</strong> 19</p>
<p><strong>Profile:</strong> Rose Labelle was employed by the Foundation in 2009 following activation of SCP-████ at [REDACTED]. Since then, Rose Labelle has maintained a low profile.</p>
<p>Any rumors spread by others pertaining to <a href="/this-is-the-real-life">anomalous expertise and feats</a> surrounding Researcher Labelle are to be discredited and reported to her immediately for investigation.</p>
<p><em>Seriously, if I find out who's been writing about these, I'm going to talk with your supervisor. The next round of these to show up in my email are being filtered into the trash. ~ Researcher Rose Labelle</em></p>
</div>
<div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none">
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-1848">SCP-1848</a> - Written by TroyL, Labelle section written by me (<a href="http://scpfoundation.ru/scp-1848">Russian Translation</a>, <a href="http://scpfoundation.123ubb.com/t5426-topic">Chinese Translation</a>)</li>
<li><a href="/scp-3860">SCP-3860</a> - Written by Jacob Conwell</li>
<li><a href="/so-it-was">So It Was</a> (Psuedo-canonical)</li>
<li><a href="/all-of-me-wants-all-of-you">All of Me Wants All of You</a></li>
<li><a href="/this-is-the-real-life">It's All True</a> - Written by thedeadlymoose (<a href="http://scpfoundation.ru/this-is-the-real-life">Russian Translation</a>) (Psuedo-canonical)</li>
<li><a href="/no-good-deed">No Good Deed</a> - Written by Jacob Conwell</li>
<li><a href="/the-blackbird-and-the-falcon">The Blackbird and The Falcon</a> - Written by Jacob Conwell</li>
<li><a href="/priorities">Priorities</a> - Written by Jacob Conwell</li>
<li><a href="/if-you-are-reading-this">If You Are Reading This...</a> - Concept/most of the article written by Jacob Conwell, &quot;To my ex&quot; written by me, canonical</li>
<li><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-2127846/decibelle-the-terrifying-cat-pattern-screamer#post-2747770">Discussion Page, Author Post</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
