<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>if inactive, ec gets custody of 2091&#160;930-j and gecko, kyun gets quiet night and birth of a new day, wjs and psul gets primae and eel, conwell gets 2906, ard gets 150, stonefish gets all of clockwork, famine/kaktus gets damej, ben gets thirty ninty, hippo gets physical world, sorver gets everything else (including thirty ninty and physical world). pb and sorver gets my drafts and permission to finish any drafts, finished or otherwise. if anyone isnt around to get custody, custody will default go to dolphinslugchugger. any of my non-collab SCPs can be rewritten if they fall low enough. none of my tales can be rewritten if they fall low enough, except for any GAW tales, which sorver gets custody of by default</p>
